FloatPoint Media Inc. is a team of highly advanced creative individuals who are dedicated to providing premiere technological solutions to our clients.

Our Growth

With 9 years in the industry we have grown to become a leading provider of custom integrated solutions to the Golden Horseshoe with international clients extending overseas.

Our Solutions

We partner with our clients to not only meet their needs, but to become an integral part of their organization in order to provide solutions which will increase their bottom line.

Our Strategy

Our strategic partnerships span over virtually every area of technology providing our clients with a network of proven organizations dedicated to the success of their project.
